---

<MainLayout title="Proxy">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Bypass blocks on your internet traffic with Holy Unblocker's web proxy."
    />
  </Fragment>
  <main>
    <div class={styles.content}>
      <h1 class={styles.title}>Ultraviolet</h1>
      <ProxyOmnibox searchEngine={Astro.locals.searchEngine} />
      <p>
        If you're having issues with the proxy, try troubleshooting your problem
        by looking at the <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Ultraviolet is <a
          class={themeStyles.themeLink}
          href={appConfig.links.github.ultraviolet}>open source</a
        > proxy software that lets you browse the internet and bypass your network
        firewall.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our servers are paid for by our premium subscribers. If you want to help
        us maintain our servers and get access to exclusive features, consider
        subscribing to
        <a class={themeStyles.themeLink} href="/sub/pricing"
          >Holy Unblocker Premium</a
        >.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a
          class={themeStyles.themeLink}
          href={appConfig.links.discord.holyunblocker}
          >Join the Holy Unblocker Discord</a
        > to talk to the community and gain access to more links.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
